description: This specially designed grey leather case stylishly protects your Canon PowerShot SD1000 digital camera while on the go, letting you take it pretty much everywhere. The case is perfect for traveling, or for everyday use of your camera, protecting it from dings and dust when you carry your camera in a pocket or purse. The grey case measures 2.5 by 4 by 1 inches (W x H x D) and weighs 0.5 pounds.
title: Canon PSC-1000 Deluxe Grey Leather Case for the Canon SD1000, SD1100IS, SD770IS and SD1200IS Digital Cameras
